 I wanted to try out Rallos to see what its like to PvP. Any advice or something special I should know first? <p><img src=C:\WINDOWS\Profiles\Scott001\Desktop\Scott\kfclwn.jpg> </img src>
<BR> Fruitiest rogue on Fennin.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uvoodoospirit.showPublicProfile?language=EN>voodoospirit</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/7/01 5:38:38 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> rz</span><hr size=1> learn fast ( usually it goes with die fast)<br>
run fast ( sow jboots)<br>
be paranoid (never say your level to hum casters?)<br>
good luck ( u will need in the 10 first levels)<br>
<br>
hehe might be short but it s the basis on RZ<br>
<br>
voodoospirit<br>
blackguard<br>
RZ <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ucoyoteblack.showPublicProfile?language=EN>coyoteblack</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/7/01 6:51:18 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: rz</span><hr size=1> Don't have any gear on. It will be taken , expect to killed for no reason. But if you make it you wont have to deal with Uber twinks, and we never have that many people on compared to Blue servers. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ulenoredamour.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Lenore Damour</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/7/01 12:14:23 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: rz</span><hr size=1> Good way to get started is to find a spot where no one else is hunting.  I have a darkelf rogue on Rallos and I started out hunting across from the city near the druid rings.  I found that no other low levels hunt there.  I also found that making friends quick is a good way to servive.  Keep good gear in the bank unless you are with your guild or a large group doing raids.  If you get PKed dont make a huge deal, after all it is a pvp server and if you tall trash to the person who killed you, you end up being there project for the rest of the night.  ( i remember a twinked, deleveled ranger had it in for me.  He would track me down all night.)<br>
Always be aware of the surroundings, use a third person view.   <br>
About twinking, since you are starting on Rallos new, you are not going to be twinking so it is not really an issue.  However, sometimes nice people give you things, easy way to keep them is bank them until you are exerianced enough to defend them or get some bags to put them in.<br>
There are tons of things to learn and know for PvP play, but you will learn them with time and experiance, and coming to the safehouse arena does not hurt.<br>
   <br>
<br>
Sincerely, <br>
Lenore D'Amour “Princess of Thieves” <br>
on Trovonnilous (Proud memeber of “Dragonmarked”)<br>
and<br>
Sabrinea Douglas <br>
Vallon Zek (Proud member of “Shanks”) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=aerimus>Aerimus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/7/01 6:08:07 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Starting over on Rallos</span><hr size=1> If your gonna play a melee don't choose Rallos, try a teams server.  Item loot bites for melees. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cylant>Cylant</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/7/01 7:11:21 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Starting over on Rallos</span><hr size=1> don't listen to angry mr. aerimus.<br>
item loot bites for casters alot more once you get a little older.. it's much easier to bag things when you're interrupting the caster, and you have 900-1k hit points.. than when you're being killed, you have 500 hit points.. and no AC. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=cylant>Cylant</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/7/01 7:17:48 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Starting over on Rallos</span><hr size=1> oh.. and a little advice would be... don't let levels 1-15 get you down... it'll get alot better.. i promise<br>
and if you need any help.. i'll be online under the name cylant.. (on rallos zek of course) if you need any help or advice.  <br>
  Oh.. and stay away from ak'anon.. greater faydark.. freeport.. neriak.. and qeynos... your safest bet for a newbie zone would probably be rivervale.. kaladin.. or halas.. no int casters are born there.. and it's a very large area.  If you do start in one of the other newbie zones, just make sure you level as fast as possible.. don't let pk'ers upset you(revenge is best served a week later).. and leave the newbie zone by level 10 at all costs.<br>
  Seriously.. don't let the pks get to you.. it'll ruin the game.. and possibly make your head explode.  Write down their name.. or /note it... and move on.  Maybe a month.. maybe a week.. maybe a day later.. you'll find them.. they won't be waiting for you, and they WILL die. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukambic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kambic</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.13thshadowcompany.com/svimages/new_post.gif BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/7/01 10:44:37 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.theglobe.com/kambic/eatdonut.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Starting over on Rallos</span><hr size=1> Shoot me a tell and I'll gove you a startup kit or whatever. First thing to save up for: Backpack.<br>
