<br>
-L <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=aerimus>Aerimus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/13/01 3:02:09 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Starting over on Rallos</span><hr size=1> Even if you win 90% of the time chances are you will end up behind in loot thats what sucks about item loot.  Either that or you'll walk around afraid to wear your gear and be less effective.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usneakythief.showPublicProfile?language=EN>sneakythief</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/14/01 9:43:38 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Starting over on Rallos</span><hr size=1> I dont have much PVP experience but i do duel any chance i get. <br>
